{"type":"message","id":"01909cb1","parentId":"fc318fbd","timestamp":"2026-06-28T10:43:37.930Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There are HTML includes files! Let me check the console.html include file which likely has the page-console HTML structure.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"有 includes 目录！看 console.html 和 devices.html。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_leva1tql5ts3q4yuvlkiiet7","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d1xxmpbsnx7medfoayxsez9q","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\devices.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":48796,"output":161,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48957,"cost":{"input":0.048796,"output":0.0005152000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0493112}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782643387234,"responseId":"cht000dca47@dx19f0dd3c5a6b9cb422"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0f09b1a5","parentId":"01909cb1","timestamp":"2026-06-28T10:43:37.941Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_leva1tql5ts3q4yuvlkiiet7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        <div class=\"page\" id=\"page-console\">\r\n            <div id=\"consoleWarning\" style=\"display:none;position:fixed;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%, -50%);background:#4a3a1a;border:2px solid #d29922;border-radius:12px;padding:32px 48px;color:#d29922;font-size:16px;z-index:10000;text-align:center;width:300px\">\r\n                <strong style=\"font-size:20px\">⚠️ 请连接设备</strong><br><br>\r\n                <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:14px\">在设备管理页面连接设备</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div id=\"ptzControlArea\">\r\n                <!-- 左右布局: 左控制, 中间画面+媒体, 右日志+画面控制 -->\r\n                <div class=\"console-layout\">\r\n                    <!-- 左: PTZ控制（整合：指向+预置点+变焦/对焦） -->\r\n                    <div class=\"console-left\">\r\n                        <!-- PTZ控制（折叠） -->\r\n                        <div class=\"collapsible-section\" id=\"ptzControlSection\">\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-header\" onclick=\"toggleSection('ptzControlSection')\">\r\n                                <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#58a6ff;margin:0\">🎯 运动控制</h3>\r\n                                <span class=\"collapse-icon\">▼</span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-content\">\r\n                                <!-- 指向控制 + 信息展示 -->\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:stretch\">\r\n                                    <!-- 左侧：方向控制 + 速度 -->\r\n                                    <div style=\"flex:0 0 auto;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between\">\r\n                                        <div class=\"ptz-controls\">\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('up-left')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('up-left')\">↖</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('up')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('up')\">↑</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('up-right')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('up-right')\">↗</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('left')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('left')\">←</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn center\">●</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('right')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('right')\">→</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('down-left')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('down-left')\">↙</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('down')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('down')\">↓</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('down-right')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('down-right')\">↘</button>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"ptz-speed\" style=\"width:170px;font-size:11px;margin-top:8px\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px\">速度:</label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"ptzSpeed\" min=\"1\" max=\"7\" value=\"4\" style=\"width:90px\">\r\n                                            <span id=\"ptzSpeedVal\" style=\"font-size:11px\">4</span>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 右侧：光圈快门 + P/T/Z（竖排，宽度减少15%） -->\r\n                                    <div style=\"flex:0 0 110px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0\">\r\n                                        <div class=\"info-block\" style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">光圈</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzIris\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">快门</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzShutter\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">R</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzWbR\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">B</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzWbB\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">空域</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzDnrSpatial\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">时域</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzDnrTemporal\">--</span></div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div style=\"border-top:2px solid #30363d;margin-top:2px;padding-top:2px\"></div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"info-block\" style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">Pan</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzPan\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">Tilt</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzTilt\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">Zoom</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzZoom\">--</span></div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <!-- 码流控制 -->\r\n                                <div class=\"section-subtitle\">码流</div>\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" id=\"btnStreamMain\" onclick=\"switchAndPlay(1)\" title=\"主码流\">主</button>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" id=\"btnStreamSub\" onclick=\"switchAndPlay(2)\" title=\"子码流\">子</button>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" id=\"btnStreamThird\" onclick=\"switchAndPlay(3)\" title=\"第三码流\">三</button>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" id=\"btnStreamStop\" onclick=\"doStopPreview()\" title=\"停止预览\">⏹</button>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <!-- 预置点 -->\r\n                                <div class=\"section-subtitle\">预置点</div>\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\r\n                                    <select id=\"ptzPresetSelect\" style=\"padding:6px 8px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:6px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:13px;min-width:120px\">\r\n                                        <option value=\"\">选择预置点</option>\r\n                                    </select>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzGotoSelectedPreset()\">前往</button>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-warning btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzSetSelectedPreset()\">保存</button>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzHome()\">归位</button>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div id=\"ptzPresetResult\" style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8b949e;text-align:center\"></div>\r\n                                <!-- 变焦/对焦 -->\r\n                                <div class=\"section-subtitle\">变焦/对焦</div>\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;margin-bottom:8px\">\r\n                                    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:13px\">焦距:</span>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('in')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('in')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">🔍+</button>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('out')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('out')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">🔍-</button>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;margin-bottom:8px\">\r\n                                    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:13px\">对焦:</span>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('near')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('near')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">远</button>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('far')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('far')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">近</button>\r\n                                    <select id=\"focusMode\" style=\"padding:4px 8px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"setFocusMode(this.value)\">\r\n                                        <option value=\"manual\">手动</option>\r\n                                        <option value=\"auto\">自动</option>\r\n                                        <option value=\"semiauto\">半自动</option>\r\n                                    </select>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <!-- 媒体信息（折叠，默认展开） -->\r\n                        <div class=\"collapsible-section\" id=\"mediaLogSection\" style=\"margin-top:12px\">\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-header\" onclick=\"toggleSection('mediaLogSection')\">\r\n                                <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#58a6ff;margin:0\">📡 媒体信息</h3>\r\n                                <span class=\"collapse-icon\">▼</span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-content\">\r\n                                <div style=\"background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:8px;padding:8px;overflow-y:auto;height:200px\">\r\n                                    <div id=\"mediaLogBox\" style=\"font-size:11px;font-family:monospace;color:#8b949e\">\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <!-- 中: 实时画面 + 媒体操作 -->\r\n                    <div class=\"console-center\">\r\n                        <div class=\"console-video-wrap\" style=\"background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:12px;overflow:hidden;position:relative;width:100%;\">\r\n                            <!-- v7.98: WASM 播放器占位区域，保留16:9比例 -->\r\n                            <div id=\"divPlugin\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;display:block;margin:0 auto\"></div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <!-- 媒体操作 + 跟踪控制 并排 -->\r\n                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;width:100%\">\r\n                            <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                <div class=\"collapsible-section\" id=\"mediaControlSection\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"collapsible-header\" onclick=\"toggleSection('mediaControlSection')\">\r\n                                        <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#3fb950;margin:0\">📷 媒体操作</h3>\r\n                                        <span class=\"collapse-icon\">▼</span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-content\">\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px\">\r\n                                    <!-- 截图/录像 -->\r\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap\">\r\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" id=\"btnConsoleSnapshot\" onclick=\"consoleSnapshot()\">📷 截图</button>\r\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-warning btn-sm\" id=\"btnConsoleRecord\" onclick=\"toggleRecord()\">⏺ 录像</button>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div id=\"consoleRecordStatus\" style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e;text-align:center\">未录像</div>\r\n                                    <!-- Live Stack -->\r\n                                    <div class=\"section-subtitle\">Live Stack 实时叠加</div>\r\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:8px\">\r\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" data-stack=\"off\" onclick=\"setLiveStackMode('off')\">关闭</button>\r\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" data-stack=\"2s\" onclick=\"setLiveStackMode('2s')\">2s</button>\r\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" data-stack=\"5s\" onclick=\"setLiveStackMode('5s')\">5s</button>\r\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" data-stack=\"10s\" onclick=\"setLiveStackMode('10s')\">10s</button>\r\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" data-stack=\"30s\" onclick=\"setLiveStackMode('30s')\">30s</button>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8b949e;text-align:center;margin-bottom:8px\">\r\n                                        硬件曝光: <input type=\"number\" id=\"hardwareExposureMs\" value=\"100\" style=\"width:60px;padding:2px 4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px\"> ms\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div class=\"btn-group\" style=\"justify-content:center\">\r\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" id=\"btnLiveStackStart\" onclick=\"startLiveStack()\">▶ 开始</button>\r\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-warning btn-sm\" id=\"btnLiveStackStop\" onclick=\"stopLiveStack()\" disabled>⏹ 停止</button>\r\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-success btn-sm\" id=\"btnLiveStackSave\" onclick=\"saveLiveStack()\" disabled>💾 保存</button>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div id=\"liveStackStatus\" style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e;text-align:center\">叠加: 关闭</div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <!-- 跟踪控制 -->\r\n                            <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                <div class=\"collapsible-section\" id=\"trackControlSection\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"collapsible-header\" onclick=\"toggleSection('trackControlSection')\">\r\n                                        <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#f0883e;margin:0\">🛤 跟踪控制</h3>\r\n                                        <span class=\"collapse-icon\">▼</span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div class=\"collapsible-content\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\r[... 56761 more characters truncated]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782643417941}}
{"type":"message","id":"af137524","parentId":"0f09b1a5","timestamp":"2026-06-28T10:43:37.941Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d1xxmpbsnx7medfoayxsez9q","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        <div class=\"page\" id=\"page-devices\">\n            <!-- 本机信息仪表盘 -->\n            <div id=\"localhostCard\" class=\"dashboard-section\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:20px\">\n                <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:16px;color:#58a6ff\">🖥️ 本机信息</h3>\n                <div class=\"dashboard-grid\" style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(6,1fr);gap:12px\">\n                    <div class=\"stat-card\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1f2e,#252d3d);border-radius:8px;padding:16px;text-align:center\">\n                        <div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e;margin-bottom:8px\">计算机名</div>\n                        <div id=\"localhost-hostname\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:#e0e6f0\">-</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"stat-card\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1f2e,#252d3d);border-radius:8px;padding:16px;text-align:center\">\n                        <div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e;margin-bottom:8px\">处理器型号</div>\n                        <div id=\"localhost-cpu\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#e0e6f0;word-break:break-all\">-</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"stat-card\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1f2e,#252d3d);border-radius:8px;padding:16px;text-align:center\">\n                        <div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e;margin-bottom:8px\">内存容量</div>\n                        <div id=\"localhost-ram\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:#58a6ff\">-</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"stat-card\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1f2e,#252d3d);border-radius:8px;padding:16px;text-align:center\">\n                        <div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e;margin-bottom:8px\">GPU型号</div>\n                        <div id=\"localhost-gpu\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#e0e6f0;word-break:break-all\">-</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"stat-card\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1f2e,#252d3d);border-radius:8px;padding:16px;text-align:center\">\n                        <div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e;margin-bottom:8px\">本机IP</div>\n                        <div id=\"localhost-ip\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:#3fb950\">-</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"stat-card\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1f2e,#252d3d);border-radius:8px;padding:16px;text-align:center\">\n                        <div style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e;margin-bottom:8px\">网关</div>\n                        <div id=\"localhost-gateway\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:#f0883e\">-</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"toolbar\">\n                <h2 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:0\">设备列表</h2>\n                <div class=\"toolbar-actions\">\n                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\" id=\"btnDiscover\" onclick=\"discoverDevices()\">\n                        <span id=\"discoverSpinner\" class=\"spinner\" style=\"display:none\"></span>\n                        🔍 发现设备\n                    </button>\n                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" onclick=\"showAddDeviceModal()\">➕ 添加设备</button>\n                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\" onclick=\"refreshDevices()\">刷新</button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <table>\n                <thead>\n                    <tr>\n                        <th>来源</th>\n                        <th>MAC</th>\n                        <th>IP</th>\n                        <th>网关</th>\n                        <th>名称</th>\n                        <th>型号</th>\n                        <th>状态</th>\n                        <th>操作</th>\n                    </tr>\n                </thead>\n                <tbody id=\"deviceTable\">\n                    <tr><td colspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center;color:#6e7681\">暂无设备</td></tr>\n                </tbody>\n            </table>\n            <!-- 设备详细信息面板 -->\n            <div id=\"deviceInfoPanel\" class=\"device-info-panel\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <!-- ==================== 主控台 ==================== -->"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782643417941}}
{"type":"message","id":"4a2f0cb2","parentId":"af137524","timestamp":"2026-06-28T10:44:12.160Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture of the codebase. Let me summarize what I've found:\n\n## Current State\n\n### Existing Modals (弹窗)\n1. **showAlert** (line 414-425) - inline style modal, click background to close\n2. **showConfirm** (line 426-442) - inline style modal, click background to close\n3. **quickAddModal** (line 1522-1536) - inline style modal, click background to close\n4. **confirmRestart** (line 2750) - uses browser `confirm()` ❌ Chrome-level dialog\n5. **resetImageControls** (in console.html) - uses browser `confirm()` ❌ Chrome-level dialog\n\n### Preset Set (预置点设置)\n- `ptzSetSelectedPreset()` (line 1283) - saves current position as preset using selected ID from dropdown\n- `presetSet()` (line 1157) - advanced page version, uses input field\n- Backend `set_preset()` in ptz.py (line 131) - supports name parameter but frontend doesn't send it\n- Backend router (line 1050-1063) - `POST /ptz/{device_id}/preset/{preset_id}/set` - only takes preset_id, no name\n\n### What needs to change:\n\n**Task 1: Add \"写入预置点\" modal to console page**\n- Replace the current \"保存\" button behavior with a modal that asks for preset ID + name\n- Need to check PTZ script's `set_preset` method - it already supports `name` parameter\n- Need to update backend API to accept name parameter\n- Need to add a new button next to \"保存\" or replace it\n\n**Task 2: Replace all Chrome-level dialogs with custom modals**\n- `confirmRestart()` uses `confirm()` → replace with custom modal\n- `resetImageControls()` uses `confirm()` → replace with custom modal\n- All existing modals: ensure they only close via ESC or cancel button, not by clicking backdrop\n\n**Task 3: Create a reusable modal component**\n- Don't duplicate inline styles everywhere\n- Single `showModal(title, content, options)` function\n- Options: showCancel, onConfirm, onCancel, etc.\n\nLet me plan the implementation:\n\n1. Create a unified modal CSS class (not inline styles)\n2. Create a unified `showModal()` function that replaces showAlert, showConfirm, quickAddModal\n3. Replace `confirm()` in confirmRestart with showModal\n4. Replace `confirm()` in resetImageControls with showModal\n5. Add \"写入预置点\" modal on console page\n6. Update backend API to accept preset name\n7. Update ptzSetSelectedPreset to use the new modal\n\nLet me now check the backend more carefully to understand the set_preset flow.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"遍历完成，已摸清全部代码。现在整理分析结果和方案。\n\n---\n\n## 代码分析\n\n### 现有弹窗（4处）\n| 位置 | 方法 | 问题 |\n|------|------|------|\n| L414 `showAlert` | 内联样式 div | 点击背景可关闭 ❌ |\n| L426 `showConfirm` | 内联样式 div | 点击背景可关闭 ❌ |\n| L1522 `quickAddModal` | 内联样式 div | 点击背景可关闭 ❌ |\n| L2750 `confirmRestart` | 浏览器 `confirm()` | Chrome级别弹窗 ❌ |\n| console.html `resetImageControls` | 浏览器 `confirm()` | Chrome级别弹窗 ❌ |\n\n### 预置点设置\n- 前端 `ptzSetSelectedPreset()` — 只用下拉框选ID，无名称输入\n- 后端 API `POST /preset/{id}/set` — 只接收 preset_id，不传 name\n- PTZ脚本 `set_preset(id, pan, tilt, zoom, name)` — **已支持 name 参数**，但前端没用\n\n---\n\n## 方案\n\n```\n统一弹窗组件 showModal(options)\n  ├── 替换 showAlert / showConfirm / quickAddModal\n  ├── 替换 confirmRestart 的 confirm()\n  ├── 替换 resetImageControls 的 confirm()\n  └── 新增 写入预置点弹窗\n       ├── 输入：预置点编号 + 名称\n       ├── 调用 set_preset(id, name=name)\n       └── 后端 API 增加 name 参数\n\n规则：\n  - ESC 关闭\n  - 取消按钮关闭\n  - 点击背景/遮罩不可关闭\n  - 弹窗打开时背景不可操作\n```\n\n先备份，然后迭代。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0rcxguv6ke1490x42g9ch4cf","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && mkdir -p backup_20260628_modal"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":71046,"output":1083,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72129,"cost":{"input":0.071046,"output":0.0034656,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0745116}},"stop