{"type":"message","id":"03856bfc","parentId":"99c52717","timestamp":"2026-06-28T10:49:37.839Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_pz17KN5ecTpLnAq2ch8V3503","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def set_preset(self, ip: str, preset_id: int) -> dict:\r\n        \"\"\"设置当前位置为预置点。\r\n\r\n        路由: POST /api/v1/ptz/{device_id}/preset/{preset_id}/set\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        ctrl, err = self._get_controller(ip)\r\n        if err:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n        success = ctrl.set_preset(preset_id)\r\n        return {\r\n            \"success\": success,\r\n            \"message\": f\"预置位 {preset_id} 设置{'成功' if success else '失败'}\",\r\n            \"preset_id\": preset_id,\r\n        }\r\n\r\n    def ptz_list_presets(self, ip: str) -> dict:\r\n        \"\"\"获取设备预置点列表。\r\n\r\n        路由: GET /api/v1/ptz/{device_id}/presets\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        ctrl, err = self._get_controller(ip)\r\n        if err:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n        presets = ctrl.list_presets()\r\n        return {\r\n            \"success\": True,\r\n            \"presets\": presets,\r\n            \"count\": len(presets),\r\n\n[291 more lines in file. Use offset=2030 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782643777839}}
{"type":"message","id":"1ed1b325","parentId":"03856bfc","timestamp":"2026-06-28T10:49:37.839Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_01_gedDDhKyTW7Xxldo1x3h9247","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/ptz/{device_id}/preset/{preset_id}/set\", summary=\"保存预置位\", tags=[\"PTZ\"])\r\nasync def ptz_set_preset(device_id: str, preset_id: int) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"设置当前位置为指定预置点。\"\"\"\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")  # type: ignore[assignment]\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    result = mgr.set_preset(target_ip, preset_id=preset_id)\r\n    if result.get(\"success\"):\r\n        log_info(\"ptz\", \"preset_set\", {\"device\": device_id, \"preset_id\": preset_id})\r\n    return result\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/ptz/{device_id}/absolute\", summary=\"绝对位置\", tags=[\"PTZ\"])\r\n\n[2969 more lines in file. Use offset=1068 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782643777839}}
{"type":"message","id":"6d69c99c","parentId":"1ed1b325","timestamp":"2026-06-28T10:50:06.413Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full picture. Let me plan the changes:\n\n1. **router.py**: Add `name` parameter to `ptz_set_preset` endpoint\n2. **ptz_controller.py**: Add `name` parameter to `set_preset` method, pass to PTZController\n3. **index.html**: \n   - Create unified `showModal()` component\n   - Replace `showAlert`, `showConfirm`, `quickAddModal`, `confirmRestart` to use it\n   - Add \"写入预置点\" button + modal in console.html\n   - Replace `resetImageControls` confirm() in console.html\n\nLet me start implementing. First, let me understand the full index.html structure to make precise edits.\n\nKey areas to modify in index.html:\n- L152-156: Modal CSS (keep, it's already defined)\n- L356: `var currentModal = null;` \n- L414-442: showAlert/showConfirm functions → replace with unified showModal\n- L1522-1560: quickAddModal → replace with showModal\n- L2750-2765: confirmRestart → replace confirm() with showModal\n\nIn console.html:\n- Add \"写入预置点\" button next to \"保存\" button\n- Replace `confirm()` in resetImageControls\n\nLet me now write the unified modal component and make all changes.\n\nThe unified modal should:\n- Create a backdrop that blocks interaction\n- Only close via ESC or cancel button\n- Support different types: alert, confirm, form\n- Be reusable\n\nLet me design the API:\n```js\nshowModal({\n  title: '标题',\n  content: '内容HTML',\n  type: 'alert' | 'confirm' | 'form',\n  onConfirm: function() {},\n  onCancel: function() {},\n  confirmText: '确定',\n  cancelText: '取消'\n});\n```\n\nFor the preset write modal, I'll use the form type or just build it as a special case.\n\nActually, let me think about this more carefully. The current approach has each modal built inline with HTML strings. The unified approach should be:\n\n1. A single `showModal(options)` function\n2. CSS for `.modal-backdrop` and `.modal` already exists\n3. ESC key handler\n4. No backdrop click close\n\nLet me implement this step by step.\n\nFor the preset write modal, the flow is:\n1. User clicks \"写入预置点\" button in console\n2. Modal opens with inputs: 编号, 名称\n3. User submits → calls API with preset_id + name\n4. Backend: router → ptz_controller → PTZController.set_preset(id, name=name)\n\nLet me now code all changes.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"开始改。先改后端，再改前端。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_zclcs4qds48qufw3zvd4e8d4","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\core\\ptz_controller.py","edits":[{"oldText":"    def set_preset(self, ip: str, preset_id: int) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"设置当前位置为预置点。\n\n        路由: POST /api/v1/ptz/{device_id}/preset/{preset_id}/set\n        \"\"\"\n        ctrl, err = self._get_controller(ip)\n        if err:\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\n\n        success = ctrl.set_preset(preset_id)\n        return {\n            \"success\": success,\n            \"message\": f\"预置位 {preset_id} 设置{'成功' if success else '失败'}\",\n            \"preset_id\": preset_id,\n        }","newText":"    def set_preset(self, ip: str, preset_id: int, name: str = \"\") -> dict:\n        \"\"\"设置当前位置为预置点。\n\n        路由: POST /api/v1/ptz/{device_id}/preset/{preset_id}/set\n        \"\"\"\n        ctrl, err = self._get_controller(ip)\n        if err:\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\n\n        success = ctrl.set_preset(preset_id, name=name)\n        return {\n            \"success\": success,\n            \"message\": f\"预置位 {preset_id} 设置{'成功' if success else '失败'}\",\n            \"preset_id\": preset_id,\n        }"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":76034,"output":1019,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77053,"cost":{"input":0.07603399999999999,"output":0.0032608000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cache