{"type":"message","id":"2677e443","parentId":"2c9eb406","timestamp":"2026-06-28T11:02:23.725Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to add a \"写入\" button next to \"保存\" in the preset section, and create the `ptzWritePreset()` function that uses the unified modal. Let me also update the existing `ptzSetSelectedPreset()` to use the new API with name parameter.\n\nLet me add the \"写入\" button in console.html:\n\n```html\n<button class=\"btn btn-warning btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzSetSelectedPreset()\">保存</button>\n<button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzWritePreset()\">写入</button>\n<button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzHome()\">归位</button>\n```\n\nAnd in index.html, I need to:\n1. Create `ptzWritePreset()` function that opens a modal with preset ID + name fields\n2. Update `ptzSetSelectedPreset()` to pass name as query param\n\nLet me also check if there are other places that use `confirm()` that I might have missed.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Now add the \"写入\" button in console.html and create the function in index.html:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2cnbw7cshjwdefea3zc4zq63","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"                                    <button class=\"btn btn-warning btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzSetSelectedPreset()\">保存</button>\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzWritePreset()\">写入</button>\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzHome()\">归位</button>","oldText":"                                    <button class=\"btn btn-warning btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzSetSelectedPreset()\">保存</button>\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzHome()\">归位</button>"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","