{"type":"message","id":"0facb243","parentId":"eab58b70","timestamp":"2026-06-28T15:43:02.142Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Everything looks good. Let me now do a final summary of all changes made.\n\nLet me verify the changes are complete:\n\n1. **Backend (router.py)**: `ptz_set_preset` now accepts `name: str = \"\"` query param, passes to mgr\n2. **Backend (ptz_controller.py)**: `set_preset` now accepts `name: str = \"\"`, passes to ctrl.set_preset(preset_id, name=name)\n3. **Frontend (index.html)**:\n   - CSS: Replaced old `.modal-backdrop`/`.modal` with unified `.astro-modal-*` classes\n   - New `showModal(options)` unified component with type: alert/confirm/form\n   - `showAlert`/`showConfirm` now delegate to `showModal` (backward compat)\n   - `showQuickAddModal` rewritten to use `showModal`\n   - `confirmRestart` rewritten to use `showModal`\n   - `deleteDevice` rewritten to use `showModal`\n   - Credential prompt rewritten to use `showModal`\n   - `addDeviceInline` rewritten to use `showModal`\n   - `modifyIpPrompt` rewritten to use `showModal`\n   - New `ptzWritePreset()` function with form modal\n   - Exposed `ptzWritePreset` to global window\n4. **Frontend (console.html)**:\n   - Added \"写入\" button next to \"保存\"\n   - `resetImageControls` confirm() replaced with showModal\n5. **Frontend (replay.html)**:\n   - `deleteSelected` confirm() replaced with showModal\n   - `filterFiles` prompt() replaced with showModal form\n\nAll Chrome-level dialogs (confirm/alert/prompt) eliminated. Unified modal with ESC + cancel button only close, backdrop click doesn't close.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"全部完成。最终扫描零残留。\n\n---\n\n## v7.117 改动总结\n\n### 改动文件（6个）\n\n| 文件 | 改动 |\n|------|------|\n| `src/api/router.py` | `/preset/{id}/set` 增加 `name` 查询参数 |\n| `src/core/ptz_controller.py` | `set_preset()` 增加 `name` 参数透传 |\n| `src/web/index.html` | 统一弹窗组件 + 替换全部7处旧弹窗 + 新增写入预置点 |\n| `src/web/includes/console.html` | 增加\"写入\"按钮 + 替换 confirm() |\n| `src/web/includes/replay.html` | 替换 confirm() + prompt() |\n| `backup_20260628_modal/` | 备份 |\n\n### 统一弹窗组件 `showModal(options)`\n\n```\noptions = {\n  type: 'alert' | 'confirm' | 'form',\n  title, message, fields, onConfirm\n}\n```\n\n- **ESC** 关闭 → `closeModal(false)`\n- **取消按钮** → `closeModal(false)`\n- **确定按钮** → `closeModal(true)` → 触发 `onConfirm`\n- **点击背景** → 不关闭（无 onclick 事件）\n- **旧接口兼容**：`showAlert`/`showConfirm` 内部委托给 `showModal`\n\n### 替换清单（10处）\n\n| 位置 | 旧方式 | 新方式 |\n|------|--------|--------|\n| 重启确认 | `confirm()` | `showModal({type:'confirm'})` |\n| 删除设备 | `confirm()` | `showModal({type:'confirm'})` |\n| 凭证输入 | `prompt()` ×2 | `showModal({type:'form'})` |\n| 添加设备(行内) | `prompt()` | `showModal({type:'form'})` |\n| 修改IP | `prompt()` | `showModal({type:'form'})` |\n| 快速添加设备 | 内联HTML | `showModal({type:'form'})` |\n| 画面重置 | `confirm()` | `showModal({type:'confirm'})` |\n| 删除文件 | `confirm()` | `showModal({type:'confirm'})` |\n| 筛选文件 | `prompt()` | `showModal({type:'form'})` |\n\n### 新增功能\n\n**写入预置点**：主控台 → 预置点区域 → \"写入\"按钮 → 弹窗输入编号+名称 → `set_preset(id, name=name)`"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":87510,"output":960,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88470,"cost":{"input":0.08750999999999999,"output":0.003072,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.090582}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782661340676,"responseId":"cht000d7b90@dx19f0ee59a62b828262"}}
