{"type":"message","id":"1ad1988f","parentId":"30775f03","timestamp":"2026-06-28T15:52:31.075Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me trace the full chain now to identify bugs. Let me look at:\n\n1. Backend API endpoint - what it returns\n2. Frontend - what it expects (`speed_map`, `speed_mapping`)\n3. How data flows from API → router → frontend\n\nLet me check the API endpoint and the loader.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"..."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_64G0rMjYkn8RlhfEBElU4415","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":2575,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":101728,"output":168,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101896,"cost":{"input":0.101728,"output":0.0005376000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1022656}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782661894049,"responseId":"cht000de27e@dx19f0eee94a9ba5e452"}}
{"type":"message","id":"dc538325","parentId":"1ad1988f","timestamp":"2026-06-28T15:52:31.080Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_64G0rMjYkn8RlhfEBElU4415","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": str(e)}\r\n\r\n\r\n# --- Speed 速度测试 ---\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/advanced/speed/run\", summary=\"运行速度测试\", tags=[\"Advanced\"])\r\nasync def advanced_speed_run(req: AdvancedSpeedRunRequest) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"运行设备速度测试 (P5.4)。\"\"\"\r\n    try:\r\n        from src.ptz.isapi.client import ISAPIClient\r\n        from src.advanced.speed import SpeedTester\r\n\r\n        # 使用传入的凭据\r\n        username = req.username or \"admin\"\r\n        password = req.password\r\n        port = req.port or 80\r\n\r\n        # 如果密码为空，尝试从PTZDeviceController获取\r\n        if not password:\r\n            mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")  # type: ignore[assignment]\r\n            if mgr:\r\n                creds = mgr.get_credentials(req.device_ip)\r\n                if creds:\r\n                    username = creds.get(\"username\", username)\r\n                    password = creds.get(\"password\", \"\")\r\n                    port = creds.get(\"port\", port)\r\n\r\n        client = ISAPIClient(ip=req.device_ip, username=username, password=password, port=port)\r\n        ptz = PTZController(client)\r\n\r\n        # 获取限位数据\r\n        from src.storage.store import get_store\r\n        store = get_store()\r\n        device_id = \"dev_001\"\r\n        limit_data = store.get_limit_results(device_id)\r\n        limit_map = limit_data.get(\"results\") if limit_data else None\r\n\r\n        # 先获取MAC\r\n        ptz_mgr_sp: \"PTZDeviceController\" = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")  # type: ignore[assignment]\r\n        mac = _resolve_mac_from_ip(req.device_ip, ptz_mgr=ptz_mgr_sp) or \"unknown\"\r\n        mac_key = mac.upper().replace(\":\", \"-\")\r\n\r\n        if not ptz.setup_home_preset():\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"HOME 预设10 设置失败(10s超时)\"}\r\n\r\n        tester = SpeedTester(ptz)\r\n        global _active_speed_tester\r\n        _active_speed_tester = tester\r\n        try:\r\n            import asyncio\r\n            results = await asyncio.to_thread(tester.run_all_tests, None, req.speed_profile)\r\n        finally:\r\n            _active_speed_tester = None\r\n\r\n        # v7.51: CSV 已通过 device_path 写入，JSON 摘要写入 mac_clean 目录\r\n        mac_clean = mac.replace(':', '').lower() if mac else \"unknown\"\r\n        config_saved = False\r\n        try:\r\n            store.save_speed_results(mac_clean, results)\r\n            config_saved = True\r\n        except Exception:\r\n            pass\r\n\r\n        return {\r\n            \"success\": results.get(\"success\", False),\r\n            \"message\": f\"速度测试完成: {req.device_ip}\",\r\n            \"results\": results,\r\n            \"config_saved\": config_saved,\r\n            \"mac\": mac,\r\n        }\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"速度测试异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n_active_speed_tester: Any = None\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/advanced/speed/cancel\", summary=\"取消速度测试\", tags=[\"Advanced\"])\r\nasync def advanced_speed_cancel(device_ip: str = Query(default=\"\")) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"取消正在运行的速度测试。\"\"\"\r\n    global _active_speed_tester\r\n    if _active_speed_tester is not None:\r\n        _active_speed_tester.cancel()\r\n        _active_speed_tester = None\r\n        return {\"success\": True, \"message\": \"速度测试已取消\"}\r\n    return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"没有正在运行的速度测试\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/advanced/speed/status\", summary=\"获取速度测试状态\", tags=[\"Advanced\"])\r\nasync def advanced_speed_status(device_ip: str = Query(default=\"\")) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取设备速度测试状态。\"\"\"\r\n    if not device_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": True, \"status\": {}}\r\n    try:\r\n        from src.ptz.isapi.client import ISAPIClient\r\n        from src.advanced.speed import SpeedTester\r\n\r\n        ptz_mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")  # type: ignore[assignment]\r\n        creds = ptz_mgr.get_credentials(device_ip) if ptz_mgr else None\r\n\n[1362 more lines in file. Use offset=2675 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782661951080}}
{"type":"message","id":"87dc9141","parentId":"dc538325","timestamp":"2026-06-28T15:52:53.149Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"  responseNow check the `renderConnectFullResults` function:","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_7Vw1deI6j7yjneP928Xh7934","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":1236,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":103020,"output":111,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103131,"cost":{"input":0.10302,"output":0.0003552,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1033752}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782661951083,"responseId":"cht000d8a1a@dx19f0eeef547b85e322"}}
{"type":"message","id":"76aba0e7","parentId":"87dc9141","timestamp":"2026-06-28T15:52:53.153Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_7Vw1deI6j7yjneP928Xh7934","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            else if (type === 'speed') html += '⚡ 速度检测完整结果';\r\n            else html += '检测结果';\r\n            html += '</h4>';\r\n            if (type === 'function') {\r\n                var funcData = results.functions || results;\r\n                html += '<table class=\"result-table\"><thead><tr><th>功能</th><th>支持</th><th>最小值</th><th>最大值</th><th>当前值</th><th>状态</th></tr></thead><tbody>';\r\n                var keys = Object.keys(funcData);\r\n                if (keys.length === 0) {\r\n                    html += '<tr><td colspan=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;color:#6e7681\">暂无结果</td></tr>';\r\n                } else {\r\n                    keys.forEach(function(key) {\r\n                        var item = funcData[key];\r\n                        if (!item || typeof item !== 'object' || !item.hasOwnProperty('supported')) return;\r\n                        var supported = item.supported ? '<span class=\"badge yes\">✅</span>' : '<span class=\"badge no\">❌</span>';\r\n                        var status = item.status || '完成';\r\n                        html += '<tr>';\r\n                        html += '<td>' + key + '</td>';\r\n                        html += '<td>' + supported + '</td>';\r\n                        html += '<td>' + (item.min_value != null ? item.min_value : '--') + '</td>';\r\n                        html += '<td>' + (item.max_value != null ? item.max_value : '--') + '</td>';\r\n                        html += '<td>' + (item.current_value != null ? item.current_value : '--') + '</td>';\r\n                        html += '<td><span class=\"badge yes\">' + status + '</span></td>';\r\n                        html += '</tr>';\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n                html += '</tbody></table>';\r\n            } else if (type === 'limit') {\r\n                html += '<div class=\"advanced-status-panel\">';\r\n                html += '<div class=\"status-row\"><span class=\"status-label\">P轴限位</span><span class=\"status-value\">' + results.pan_min + ' ~ ' + results.pan_max + '</span></div>';\r\n                html += '<div class=\"status-row\"><span class=\"status-label\">T轴限位</span><span class=\"status-value\">' + results.tilt_min + ' ~ ' + results.tilt_max + '</span></div>';\r\n                html += '<div class=\"status-row\"><span class=\"status-label\">Z轴限位</span><span class=\"status-value\">' + results.zoom_min + ' ~ ' + results.zoom_max + '</span></div>';\r\n                html += '<div class=\"status-row\"><span class=\"status-label\">翻转</span><span class=\"status-value\">' + (results.has_flip ? '有' : '无') + '</span></div>';\r\n                html += '<div class=\"status-row\"><span class=\"status-label\">稳定性</span><span class=\"status-value\">' + (results.stability_check ? '<span class=\"badge yes\">✅ 稳定</span>' : '<span class=\"badge no\">❌ 不稳定</span>') + '</span></div>';\r\n                if (results.csv_path) html += '<div class=\"status-row\"><span class=\"status-label\">CSV 路径</span><span class=\"status-value\">' + results.csv_path + '</span></div>';\r\n                html += '</div>';\r\n            } else if (type === 'speed') {\r\n                var speedMap = results.speed_map || results.speed_mapping || {};\r\n                html += _renderSpeedTable('📊 总体', speedMap);\r\n                var panMap = results.pan_speed || {};\r\n                html += _renderSpeedTable('🔵 Pan轴', panMap);\r\n                var tiltMap = results.tilt_speed || {};\r\n                html += _renderSpeedTable('🟠 Tilt轴', tiltMap);\r\n                html += '<div class=\"advanced-status-panel\">';\r\n                html += '<div class=\"status-row\"><span class=\"status-label\">测试总数</span><span class=\"status-value\">' + (results.total_tests || '--') + '</span></div>';\r\n                html += '</div>';\r\n            }\r\n            html += '</div>';\r\n            // Append rather than replace to show all test results\r\n            area.innerHTML += html;\r\n        }\r\n        // ================================================================\r\n        // ================================================================\r\n        //  预置点列表管理 (主控台版)\r\n        // ================================================================\r\n        function loadPresetList() {\r\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n            if (!dev) return;\r\n            var resultDiv = document.getElementById('ptzPresetResult');\r\n            var sel = document.getElementById('ptzPresetSelect');\r\n            if (!sel) return;  // Not on console page\r\n            if (resultDiv) resultDiv.textContent = '正在获取预置点列表...';\r\n            apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/presets').then(function(resp) {\r\n                sel.innerHTML = '<option value=\"\">选择预置点</option>';\r\n                if (resp && resp.success && resp.presets && resp.presets.length > 0) {\r\n                    resp.presets.forEach(function(p) {\r\n                        var opt = document.createElement('option');\r\n                        opt.value = p.id;\r\n                        opt.textContent = p.name ? ('P' + p.id + ' - ' + p.name) : '预置点 ' + p.id;\r\n                        sel.appendChild(opt);\r\n                    });\r\n                    if (resultDiv) resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#3fb950\">已加载 ' + resp.presets.length + ' 个预置点</span>';\r\n                } else {\r\n                    if (resultDiv) resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#d29922\">未获取到预置点</span>';\r\n                }\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                if (resultDiv) resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#f85149\">获取失败: ' + e.message + '</span>';\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n        function ptzGotoSelectedPreset() {\r\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice.ip;\r\n            var sel = document.getElementById('ptzPresetSelect');\r\n            var presetId = parseInt(sel.value);\r\n            if (!dev) { showToast('warning', '请先选择设备'); return; }\r\n            if (!presetId) { showToast('warning', '请先选择预置点'); return; }\r\n            var resultDiv = document.getElementById('ptzPresetResult');\r\n            resultDiv.textContent = '跳转到预置点 ' + presetId + '...';\r\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/preset/' + presetId, null).then(function(resp) {\r\n                if (resp && resp.success !== false) {\r\n                    resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#3fb950\">✅ 已前往预置点 ' + presetId + '</span>';\r\n                    if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('预置点: 前往 #' + presetId, 'success');\r\n                } else {\r\n                    resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#f85149\">❌ 跳转失败: ' + (resp ? resp.message : '未知') + '</span>';\r\n                }\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#f85149\">❌ 异常: ' + e.message + '</span>';\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n        function ptzSetSelectedPreset() {\r\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice.ip;\r\n            var sel = document.getElementById('ptzPresetSelect');\r\n\n[1882 more lines in file. Use offset=1336 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782661973153}}
{"type":"message","id":"2b422323","parentId":"76aba0e7","timestamp":"2026-06-28T15:53:56.578Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"  responseNow I have a thorough understanding. Let me analyze the bugs:\n\n## 速度测试分析\n\n### 后端 `post_process_csv` 返回的数据结构\n\n```python\n{\"axis\", \"direction\", \"speed_level\", \"speed_val\", \"hit_limit\", \"zoom\", \"repeats\", \"movement_direction\", \"direction_info\", \"mac\"}\n```\n\n关键字段：`axis`, `direction`, `speed_level`, `zoom`, `speed_val`（单位：°/s）。\n\n### 前端渲染 Bug\n\n**Bug 1：前端期待 `speed_map`/`speed_mapping`，但后端返回的是 `results` 数组**\n\n`renderSpeedResults()` 和 `renderConnectFullResults()` 都读取：\n```js\nvar speedMap = results.speed_map || results.speed_mapping || {};\nvar panMap = results.pan_speed || {};\nvar tiltMap = results.tilt_speed || {};\n```\n\n但 `run_all_tests()` 返回的是 `list[dict]` 数组，没有 `speed_map`/`pan_speed`/`tilt_speed` 顶层键。\n\n**Bug 2：router.py 第 2636 行 `results.get(\"success\")` 在数组上调用**\n\n```python\nreturn {\n    \"results\": results,  # results 是 list[dict]\n}\n```\n而 `results.get(\"success\")` 会把 list 当作 dict 取值，永远返回 `None`（falsy）。\n\n**Bug 3：`speedProfile` 选择器的值可能未被读取**\n\n需要确认前端是否有速度 profile 选择器传值。\n\n**Bug 4：前端 speed 结果显示为空**\n\n因为渲染函数期待 `speed_map` 格式但 `results` 数组里没有这个 key，`renderConnectSpeedResultMini` 里 `Object.keys(speedMap).length` = 0。\n\n### 具体 Bug 列表\n\n| # | 位置 | 问题 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | `router.py:2636` | `results.get(\"success\")` 对 `list` 调 `.get()`，永远 None |\n| 2 | `index.html:renderSpeedResults` | 期待 `speed_map`/`pan_speed`/`tilt_speed` 顶层key，后端没有构建这些 |\n| 3 | `index.html:renderConnectSpeedResultMini` | 同上，`Object.keys(speedMap).length` = 0 |\n| 4 | `index.html:renderConnectFullResults(speed)` | 同上 |\n| 5 | `router.py:2628` | `results` 是 `list[dict]`，但返回时包装成 `\"results\": results`，前端同时收到 `resp.results` 是数组 |\n\n修复后需要：前端渲染函数按 `results` 数组格式分组为 `speed_map`/`pan_speed`/`tilt_speed`。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"老板，速度测试分析完了：\n\n---\n\n## Bug 清单\n\n| # | 严重 | 位置 | 问题 |\n|---|------|------|------|\n| 🔴 1 | **致命** | `router.py:2636` | `results.get(\"success\")` — `results` 是 `list`，`.get()` 永远 `None`，API 始终返回 `success: false` |\n| 🔴 2 | **致命** | `index.html:renderSpeedResults` | 期待 `speed_map`/`pan_speed`/`tilt_speed` 顶层 key，但后端返回的是 `results` 数组，渲染永远为空 |\n| 🔴 3 | **致命** | `index.html:renderConnectSpeedResultMini` | 同上，`Object.keys(speedMap).length` = 0 → 显示\"0 个速度档位\" |\n| 🔴 4 | **致命** | `index.html:renderConnectFullResults` | 同上，速度表格永远不显示 |\n\n**根因**：`post_process_csv` 正确返回 `list[dict]`（含 `axis`/`direction`/`speed_level`/`zoom`/`speed_val`），但前端渲染按旧格式 `{speed_map:{...}, pan_speed:{...}, tilt_speed:{...}}` 读，数据到不了手。\n\n---\n\n## 修复方案\n\n```\nrouter.py: 返回前将 results 数组分组为 {speed_map, pan_speed, tilt_speed}\n前端: 无需改，渲染函数逻辑正确（只是数据结构不匹配）\n```\n\n需要我修复吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":105020,"output":975,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105995,"cost":{"input":0.10501999999999999,"output":0.0031200000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.10813999999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782661973156,"responseId":"cht000f8696@dx19f0eef4045ba5d452"}}
