{"type":"message","id":"05018268","parentId":"0972a774","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:30:09.801Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_01_0YjjWkWxE8CtO9JNGHXw6782","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                html += results.pan_has_limit ? '<span style=\"color:#3fb950\">✓ 是</span>' : '<span style=\"color:#f85149\">✗ 否</span>';\r\n                html += '</div>';\r\n            }\r\n            if (results.has_flip !== undefined) {\r\n                html += '<div style=\"margin-top:4px\">';\r\n                html += '<span style=\"color:#8b949e\">T轴（垂直）自动翻转：</span> ';\r\n                html += results.has_flip ? '<span style=\"color:#3fb950\">✓ 是</span>' : '<span style=\"color:#f85149\">✗ 否</span>';\r\n                html += '</div>';\r\n            }\r\n            html += '</div>';\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        resultEl.innerHTML = html;\r\n    } else if (results.speed_map !== undefined || results.pan_speed !== undefined) {\r\n        // 速度测试结果\r\n        let html = '<div style=\"font-size:12px\">';\r\n        html += '<div style=\"margin-bottom:8px;font-weight:600;color:#58a6ff\">⚡ 速度测试结果</div>';\r\n        html += '<div style=\"margin-bottom:8px;color:#8b949e\">';\r\n        html += '档位: <b>' + (results.speed_profile || '-') + '</b> | ';\r\n        html += '测试数: <b>' + (results.total_tests || 0) + '</b>';\r\n        html += '</div>';\r\n        \r\n        // Speed table\r\n        if (results.pan_speed || results.tilt_speed) {\r\n            html += '<table style=\"width:100%;font-size:11px;border-collapse:collapse;margin-top:8px\">';\r\n            html += '<tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d\"><th style=\"text-align:left;padding:4px\">速度档位</th><th style=\"text-align:center;padding:4px\">Pan (°/s)</th><th style=\"text-align:right;padding:4px\">Tilt (°/s)</th></tr>';\r\n            \r\n            const panSpeed = results.pan_speed || {};\r\n            const tiltSpeed = results.tilt_speed || {};\r\n            const allLevels = new Set([...Object.keys(panSpeed), ...Object.keys(tiltSpeed)]);\r\n            \r\n            for (const level of Array.from(allLevels).sort((a,b) => a - b)) {\r\n                html += '<tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #21262d\">';\r\n                html += '<td style=\"padding:4px\">' + level + '</td>';\r\n                html += '<td style=\"text-align:center;padding:4px\">' + (panSpeed[level] || '-') + '</td>';\r\n                html += '<td style=\"text-align:right;padding:4px\">' + (tiltSpeed[level] || '-') + '</td>';\r\n                html += '</tr>';\r\n            }\r\n            html += '</table>';\r\n        }\r\n        html += '</div>';\r\n        resultEl.innerHTML = html;\r\n    } else {\r\n        // 功能测试结果\r\n        let html = '<table style=\"width:100%;font-size:11px;border-collapse:collapse\">';\r\n        html += '<tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d\"><th style=\"text-align:left;padding:4px\">项目</th><th style=\"text-align:center;padding:4px\">支持</th><th style=\"text-align:right;padding:4px\">范围</th></tr>';\r\n\r\n        for (const [key, val] of Object.entries(results)) {\r\n            if (typeof val === 'object' && val !== null) {\r\n                const label = val.label || key;\r\n                const supported = val.supported ? 'Y' : 'N';\r\n                // v7.52: 兼容两种字段名：min/min_val, max/max_val\r\n                const range = (val.min || val.min_val || '-') + '~' + (val.max || val.max_val || '-');\r\n                html += '<tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #21262d\"><td style=\"padding:4px\">' + label + '</td><td style=\"text-align:center;padding:4px\">' + supported + '</td><td style=\"text-align:right;padding:4px\">' + range + '</td></tr>';\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        html += '</table>';\r\n        resultEl.innerHTML = html;\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 更新视频状态\r\nfunction updateAdvVideoStatus() {\r\n    const statusEl = document.getElementById('advVideoStatus');\r\n    if (window.connectedDevice && window.connectedDevice.ip) {\r\n        if (statusEl) statusEl.textContent = '\\u5df2\\u8fde\\u63a5: ' + (window.connectedDevice.name || window.connectedDevice.device_name || window.connectedDevice.ip);\r\n    } else {\r\n        if (statusEl) statusEl.textContent = '连接设备后显示实时画面';\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 天文校准功能\r\nlet astroCalSession = null;\r\nlet astroCalMethod = 'manual'; // 'manual' or 'auto'\r\n\r\nfunction startAstroCalibration(deviceIp, username, password) {\r\n    addAdvOutput('info', '启动天文校准...');\r\n    \r\n    // 获取观测站位置（从配置或默认值）\r\n\n[387 more lines in file. Use offset=475 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782675009801}}
{"type":"message","id":"037d8d01","parentId":"05018268","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:30:22.580Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found the issue. The `advanced.html` has its own rendering path for speed results. Let me trace the full flow:\n\n1. User clicks \"开始测试\" in advanced.html → calls `runAdvTest()`\n2. `runAdvTest()` sends the API request and gets back the response\n3. The response is rendered by `renderAdvResult()` in advanced.html\n4. `renderAdvResult()` checks `results.speed_map !== undefined || results.pan_speed !== undefined` to detect speed results\n\nThe problem: `advanced.html`'s `renderAdvResult()` is the one that shows the \"项目 支持 范围\" table for speed results. Let me check how the response flows through `runAdvTest()`.\n\nLet me read the `runAdvTest()` function and `renderAdvResult()` more carefully.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"...\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_x3x5wcv774m3vqmzweh8g9e6","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":260,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\advanced.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":128682,"output":272,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128954,"cost":{"input":0.128682,"output":0.0008704000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.12955239999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782675009804,"responseId":"cht000db684@dx19f0fb5f379b91a122"}}
