{"type":"message","id":"316e31f5","parentId":"97799adc","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:30:36.274Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" 响应现在看清楚完整链路：\n\n1. `advanced.html` 的 `runAdvTest()` → 调用 `/api/v1/advanced/detect/start` → 异步轮询 → `renderAdvResult()`\n2. `index.html` 的 `speedTestRun()` → 调用 `/api/v1/advanced/speed/run` → 直接 `renderSpeedResults()`\n\n问题出在 `advanced.html` 的渲染逻辑 `renderAdvResult()` 和 `/api/v1/advanced/detect/start` API。让我看看 detect API 怎么处理 speed 结果。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"..."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_8aVf4Q2DzuElIeSDgBEN7343","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && Select-String -Path src/api/router.py -Pattern \"detect.*start|detect.*task|detect.*speed|def.*detect\" -AllMatches | Select-Object -First 20 LineNumber,Line"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":130478,"output":233,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130711,"cost":{"input":0.13047799999999998,"output":0.0007456,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1312236}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782675031202,"responseId":"cht000d5336@dx19f0fb6464fb85e322"}}
