{"type":"message","id":"564fcf6e","parentId":"ba143b5d","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:30:40.001Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_0kJidebja3e9nx5TW96Z6534","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                limit_tester = LimitTester(client, device_id=device_id)\r\n                # v7.56: 添加进度回调\r\n                def limit_progress_callback(step_name: str, completed: int, result: str = \"\"):\r\n                    detect_tasks[task_id][\"current_step\"] = step_name\r\n                    detect_tasks[task_id][\"completed_items\"] = completed\r\n                    detect_tasks[task_id][\"last_result\"] = result\r\n                limit_result = await asyncio.to_thread(limit_tester.run_all_tests, limit_progress_callback)\r\n                if not limit_result.get(\"success\"):\r\n                    detect_tasks[task_id].update(status=\"failed\", current_step=f\"limit: {limit_result.get('message', limit_result.get('error', '未知错误'))}\")\r\n                    return\r\n                results[\"limit\"] = limit_result\r\n                detect_tasks[task_id].update(progress=60.0, completed_items=3)\r\n                write_device_config(mac=mac, limits=limit_result, ip=req.device_ip)\r\n\r\n            if \"speed\" in req.items:\r\n                from src.advanced.speed import SpeedTester\r\n\r\n                if _cancelled(): return\r\n                detect_tasks[task_id].update(progress=65.0, current_step=\"speed_test\", total_items=0, completed_items=0)\r\n                if not PTZController(client).setup_home_preset():\r\n                    detect_tasks[task_id].update(status=\"failed\", current_step=\"speed: HOME预设10设置失败(10s超时)\")\r\n                    return\r\n                speed_tester = SpeedTester(PTZController(client))\r\n                # v7.56: 添加进度回调\r\n                def speed_progress_callback(step_name: str, completed: int, total: int, result: str = \"\"):\r\n                    detect_tasks[task_id][\"current_step\"] = step_name\r\n                    detect_tasks[task_id][\"completed_items\"] = completed\r\n                    detect_tasks[task_id][\"total_items\"] = total\r\n                    detect_tasks[task_id][\"last_result\"] = result\r\n                speed_result = await asyncio.to_thread(speed_tester.run_all_tests, None, req.speed_profile, speed_progress_callback)\r\n                if not speed_result:\r\n                    detect_tasks[task_id].update(status=\"failed\", current_step=\"speed: 无结果\")\r\n                    return\r\n                results[\"speed\"] = speed_result\r\n                detect_tasks[task_id].update(progress=95.0)\r\n                write_device_config(mac=_resolve_mac_from_ip(req.device_ip, ptz_mgr=mgr), speed=speed_result, ip=req.device_ip)\r\n\r\n            detect_tasks[task_id].update(\r\n                status=\"completed\",\r\n                progress=100.0,\r\n                current_step=\"completed\",\r\n                results=results,\r\n            )\r\n        except Exception as e:\r\n            detect_tasks[task_id].update(status=\"failed\", current_step=str(e), progress=0.0)\r\n\r\n    asyncio.create_task(_run_detect())\r\n\r\n    return {\r\n        \"success\": True,\r\n        \"task_id\": task_id,\r\n        \"message\": \"检测任务已启动\",\r\n    }\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/advanced/detect/status/{task_id}\", summary=\"获取检测任务状态\", tags=[\"Advanced\"])\r\nasync def advanced_detect_status(task_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取一键检测任务进度。\"\"\"\r\n    task = detect_tasks.get(task_id)\r\n    if not task:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"任务不存在\"}\r\n    return {\r\n        \"success\": True,\r\n        \"status\": task[\"status\"],\r\n        \"progress\": task.get(\"progress\", 0.0),\r\n        \"current_step\": task.get(\"current_step\", \"\"),\r\n        \"completed_items\": task.get(\"completed_items\", 0),\r\n        \"total_items\": task.get(\"total_items\", 0),\r\n        \"last_result\": task.get(\"last_result\", \"\"),\r\n    }\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/advanced/detect/result/{task_id}\", summary=\"获取检测结果\", tags=[\"Advanced\"])\r\nasync def advanced_detect_result(task_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取一键检测最终结果。\"\"\"\r\n    task = detect_tasks.get(task_id)\r\n    if not task:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"任务不存在\"}\r\n    if task[\"status\"] != \"completed\":\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"任务尚未完成: {task['status']}\"}\r\n    return {\r\n        \"success\": True,\r\n        \"results\": task.get(\"results\", {}),\r\n    }\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/advanced/detect/cancel/{task_id}\", summary=\"取消检测任务\", tags=[\"Advanced\"])\r\nasync def advanced_detect_cancel(task_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"取消正在运行的一键检测任务。\"\"\"\r\n    task = detect_tasks.get(task_id)\r\n    if not task:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"任务不存在\"}\r\n    if task[\"status\"] not in (\"running\",):\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"任务状态为 {task['status']}，无法取消\"}\r\n    task[\"status\"] = \"cancelled\"\r\n    task[\"current_step\"] = \"cancelled\"\r\n    return {\"success\": True, \"message\": \"任务已取消\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n# --- Config 配置 ---\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/advanced/config/{mac}\", summary=\"获取设备配置\", tags=[\"Advanced\"])\r\nasync def advanced_get_config(mac: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取设备配置文件。\"\"\"\r\n    try:\r\n        from src.advanced.config_writer import load_device_config, list_device_configs\r\n\r\n        if mac == \"all\":\r\n            configs = list_device_configs()\r\n            return {\r\n                \"success\": True,\r\n                \"data\": configs,\r\n                \"total\": len(configs),\r\n            }\r\n\r\n        config = load_device_config(mac)\r\n        if config:\r\n            return {\r\n                \"success\": True,\r\n                \"data\": config.to_dict(),\r\n\n[1125 more lines in file. Use offset=2945 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782675040001}}
{"type":"message","id":"d162c008","parentId":"564fcf6e","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:30:44.799Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" 响应Now I see the full picture. The `advanced.html` speed test flow goes through `detect/start` API, which calls `speed_tester.run_all_tests()` directly and stores the raw `list` result in `results[\"speed\"]` — **without** the formatting that `advanced_speed_run` does. Then `renderAdvResult` in `advanced.html` reads `results.speed_map` which is undefined for the raw list.\n\nLet me trace the renderAdvResult function to confirm:","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到根因了。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_BHmcJvl4M5VtiKLIntvU4304","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":366,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\advanced.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":132739,"output":211,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132950,"cost":{"input":0.132739,"output":0.0006752,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.13341419999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782675040005,"responseId":"cht000ead75@dx19f0fb668beb87f332"}}
{"type":"message","id":"27195f1b","parentId":"d162c008","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:30:44.804Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_BHmcJvl4M5VtiKLIntvU4304","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function renderAdvResult(data) {\r\n    const resultEl = document.getElementById('advResult');\r\n    // v7.52: 修复字段名不匹配：后端返回 functions（不是 results）\r\n    const results = data.functions || data.results || data;\r\n\r\n    // 检测结果类型\r\n    if (results.pan_min !== undefined || results.tilt_min !== undefined) {\r\n        // 限位测试结果\r\n        let html = '<table style=\"width:100%;font-size:11px;border-collapse:collapse\">';\r\n        html += '<tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d\"><th style=\"text-align:left;padding:4px\">轴</th><th style=\"text-align:center;padding:4px\">下限</th><th style=\"text-align:right;padding:4px\">上限</th></tr>';\r\n\r\n        if (results.pan_min !== undefined) {\r\n            html += '<tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #21262d\"><td style=\"padding:4px\">P轴</td><td style=\"text-align:center;padding:4px\">' + results.pan_min + '</td><td style=\"text-align:right;padding:4px\">' + results.pan_max + '</td></tr>';\r\n        }\r\n        if (results.tilt_min !== undefined) {\r\n            html += '<tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #21262d\"><td style=\"padding:4px\">T轴</td><td style=\"text-align:center;padding:4px\">' + results.tilt_min + '</td><td style=\"text-align:right;padding:4px\">' + results.tilt_max + '</td></tr>';\r\n        }\r\n        if (results.zoom_min !== undefined) {\r\n            html += '<tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #21262d\"><td style=\"padding:4px\">Z轴</td><td style=\"text-align:center;padding:4px\">' + results.zoom_min + '</td><td style=\"text-align:right;padding:4px\">' + results.zoom_max + '</td></tr>';\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        html += '</table>';\r\n\r\n        // v7.54: P轴限位状态 + T轴翻转状态\r\n        if (results.pan_has_limit !== undefined || results.has_flip !== undefined) {\r\n            html += '<div style=\"margin-top:8px;padding:8px;background:#161b22;border-radius:4px\">';\r\n            if (results.pan_has_limit !== undefined) {\r\n                html += '<div>';\r\n                html += '<span style=\"color:#8b949e\">P轴（水平）限位：</span> ';\r\n                html += results.pan_has_limit ? '<span style=\"color:#3fb950\">✓ 是</span>' : '<span style=\"color:#f85149\">✗ 否</span>';\r\n\n[466 more lines in file. Use offset=396 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782675044804}}
{"type":"compaction","id":"c3ce34b1","parentId":"27195f1b","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:32:04.027Z","summary":"## Goal\n用户要求修改 AstroHub 的页面弹窗：\n1. 给主控台增加\"写入预置点\"弹窗，输入编号和名称，检查 PTZ 脚本中 `set_preset` 的方法\n2. 修改所有弹窗样式：设备管理手动添加设备、重启确认、输入预置点等，都不能使用 Chrome 级别的弹窗（alert/confirm/prompt），而是页面上弹出窗口，只能按 ESC 或点击取消按钮关闭，背景区域不可操作\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- 禁止过度开发\n- 禁止打补丁开发\n- 保持代码干净，做好复用关系\n- 先遍历代码再开发\n\n[Compaction summary truncated to fit budget]\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Goal\n修复速度测试功能中的多个 bug：后端返回格式错误（`results` 是 list 而非 dict）、前端 `success:false` 时未在结果区域显示错误、数据分组缺失 zoom 维度。\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- 禁止过度开发，禁止打补丁\n- 精确修复，除非必要不引入额外变量、额外库、额外脚本\n- 修复前先备份\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] 备份文件到 `backup_20260628_modal/`（`router.py`, `index.html`, `speed.py`）\n- [x] `router.py:2631-2645` — 修复 `results.get(\"success\")`（list 无 `.get()` 方法），将 list 结果分组为 `{speed_map, pan_speed, tilt_speed, by_zoom, total_tests}` 格式\n- [x] `index.html:920-925` — `speedTestRun()` 中 `success:false` 时在 `speedResultArea` 显示错误信息\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] 验证前端渲染函数 `renderSpeedResults`、`renderConnectSpeedResultMini`、`renderConnectFullResults` 是否与新数据格式兼容\n- [ ] 确认 `connectSpeedTestRun` 的 `success:false` 错误显示是否已完备\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **分组逻辑在 router.py 中完成**：不在 `speed.py` 的 `run_all_tests` 中修改（避免破坏 CLI 独立使用），而是在 API 返回前将 list 转为 dict\n- **`by_zoom` 数据格式**：`{zoom: {axis: {speed_level: speed_val}}}`，作为响应的一部分返回但暂不修改前端渲染 UI\n- **speed_map/pan_speed/tilt_speed 均为各 zoom 值的平均值**\n\n## Next Steps\n1. 验证 `renderSpeedResults` 读取 `results.speed_map/pan_speed/tilt_speed/total_tests` 是否正常工作\n2. 确认 `connectSpeedTestRun` 的 `success:false` 分支已更新 `connectFullResultArea`（当前只更新了 `connectSpeedResultMini`）\n3. 测试完整流程\n\n## Critical Context\n- **文件路径**：`C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py`（约 2631 行）、`src\\web\\index.html`（约 920 行）\n- **数据流**：`SpeedTester.run_all_tests()` → `post_process_csv()` 返回 `list[dict]`（每个 dict 含 axis/direction/speed_