{"type":"message","id":"0290c849","parentId":"1f56aae9","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:34:44.882Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to fix the frontend `renderAdvResult` in `advanced.html` to handle the new speed format. Currently it checks for `results.speed_map` or `results.pan_speed` to identify speed results, and renders a table. But the issue is that `data` comes from the detect API as `{results: {speed: {...}}}` and `renderAdvResult` is called with the test result for each item.\n\nLet me check how `renderAdvResult` is called from `pollAdvProgress`:","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在修前端 `advanced.html` 的 `renderAdvResult`：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_h14vu14qv78my9jpe778g1qt","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":746,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\advanced.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":47377,"output":225,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47602,"cost":{"input":0.047376999999999996,"output":0.00072,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.048096999999999994}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782675277073,"responseId":"cht000db93e@dx19f0fba0639b828262"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2769fdbc","parentId":"0290c849","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:34:44.899Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_h14vu14qv78my9jpe778g1qt","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"var advPollInterval = null;\r\nvar advTaskId = null;\r\n\r\nfunction pollAdvProgress(taskId) {\r\n    advTaskId = taskId;\r\n    var progressEl = document.getElementById('advProgress');\r\n    var pollUrl = '/api/v1/advanced/detect/status/' + taskId;\r\n    \r\n    // 清除之前的轮询\r\n    if (advPollInterval) clearInterval(advPollInterval);\r\n    \r\n    // v7.53: 添加去重逻辑，避免重复输出\r\n    var lastStep = '';\r\n    \r\n    advPollInterval = setInterval(function() {\r\n        fetch(pollUrl)\r\n        .then(r => r.json())\r\n        .then(data => {\r\n            if (data.success) {\r\n                // v7.52: 后端返回的字段直接在根级别（没有task包裹）\r\n                var progress = data.progress || 0;\r\n                var step = data.current_step || 'running';\r\n                var status = data.status || 'running';\r\n                \r\n                // v7.52: 更新进度显示（N/M格式）\r\n                var completedItems = data.completed_items || 0;\r\n                var totalItems = data.total_items || 0;\r\n                if (progressEl) {\r\n                    if (totalItems > 0) {\r\n                        progressEl.textContent = currentAdvTest + ' (' + completedItems + '/' + totalItems + ')';\r\n                    } else {\r\n                        progressEl.textContent = currentAdvTest + ' ' + progress.toFixed(0) + '%';\r\n                    }\r\n                }\r\n                \r\n                // v7.53: 实时输出当前检测端点（去重：只在步骤变化时输出）\r\n                if (step && step !== 'running' && step !== 'completed' && step !== lastStep) {\r\n                    var lastResult = data.last_result || '';\r\n                    addAdvOutput(lastResult === 'pass' ? 'success' : (lastResult === 'failed' ? 'error' : 'info'), \r\n                        '检测端点: ' + step + '...' + (lastResult || ''));\r\n                    lastStep = step;\r\n                }\r\n                \r\n                // v7.53: 检查是否完成（使用getElementById获取按钮，因为是局部变量）\r\n                if (status === 'completed') {\r\n                    clearInterval(advPollInterval);\r\n                    advTaskId = null;\r\n                    addAdvOutput('success', '测试完成');\r\n                    document.getElementById('btnAdvRun').disabled = false;\r\n                    document.getElementById('btnAdvStop').disabled = true;\r\n                    // v7.54: 恢复其他页面标签\r\n                    document.querySelectorAll('.nav-btn[data-page]').forEach(function(btn) {\r\n                        btn.disabled = false;\r\n                        btn.style.opacity = '';\r\n                        btn.style.cursor = '';\r\n                    });\r\n                    // 获取最终结果\r\n                    fetchResult(taskId);\r\n                } else if (status === 'failed') {\r\n                    clearInterval(advPollInterval);\r\n                    advTaskId = null;\r\n                    addAdvOutput('error', '测试失败: ' + step);\r\n                    document.getElementById('btnAdvRun').disabled = false;\r\n                    document.getElementById('btnAdvStop').disabled = true;\r\n                    // v7.54: 恢复其他页面标签\r\n                    document.querySelectorAll('.nav-btn[data-page]').forEach(function(btn) {\r\n                        btn.disabled = false;\r\n                        btn.style.opacity = '';\r\n                        btn.style.cursor = '';\r\n                    });\r\n                    if (progressEl) progressEl.textContent = currentAdvTest + ' 失败';\r\n                } else if (status === 'cancelled') {\r\n                    clearInterval(advPollInterval);\r\n                    advTaskId = null;\r\n                    addAdvOutput('warn', '测试已取消');\r\n                    document.getElementById('btnAdvRun').disabled = false;\r\n                    document.getElementById('btnAdvStop').disabled = true;\r\n                    document.querySelectorAll('.nav-btn[data-page]').forEach(function(btn) {\r\n                        btn.disabled = false;\r\n                        btn.style.opacity = '';\r\n                        btn.style.cursor = '';\r\n                    });\r\n                    if (progressEl) progressEl.textContent = '';\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n        })\r\n        .catch(e => {\r\n            console.error('Poll error:', e);\r\n        });\r\n    }, 1000); // 每1秒轮询一次\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction fetchResult(taskId) {\r\n    var resultUrl = '/api/v1/advanced/detect/result/' + taskId;\r\n    fetch(resultUrl)\r\n    .then(r => r.json())\r\n    .then(data => {\r\n        if (data.success && data.results) {\r\n            // v7.52: 从总结果中取当前测试类型的结果\r\n            var testResult = data.results[currentAdvTest] || data.results;\r\n\n[16 more lines in file. Use offset=846 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782675284899}}
