{"type":"message","id":"115c8f7a","parentId":"006faaf3","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:36:17.494Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me verify the complete fix:\n\n1. **Root cause**: `advanced.html` → `detect/start` API stores `run_all_tests()` raw list → `renderAdvResult` sees no `speed_map`/`pan_speed` → falls through to \"功能测试\" branch → shows \"项目 支持 范围\" table with raw dict keys\n\n2. **Fix applied**:\n   - `router.py`: Added `_format_speed_results()` shared function, used in both `/advanced/speed/run` and `detect/start`\n   - `advanced.html`: Fixed `fetchResult` to handle `total_tests` for speed count\n\n3. **`renderAdvResult` already handles the formatted data** — it checks `results.speed_map !== undefined || results.pan_speed !== undefined` which will now be true after the backend fix.\n\nLet me restart astrohub and verify.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"语法OK。重启验证：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_xd3fj2b981uyiah0enmdo9ix","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Process python -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Stop-Process -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue; Start-Sleep 2; cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub; Start-Process python -ArgumentList \"-m src.main.main --headless\" -NoNewWindow; Start-Sleep 5; (Invoke-WebRequest -Uri \"http://127.0.0.1:10280/api/v1/localhost\" -UseBasicParsing -TimeoutSec 5).StatusCode"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":52433,"output":353,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52786,"cost":{"input":0.052433,"output":0.0011296000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0535626}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782675364294,"responseId":"cht000dd4b1@dx19f0fbb5a9ab9ca422"}}
