{"type":"message","id":"b6e77ed0","parentId":"ad4594ba","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:36:50.536Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is the `while True` in a one-liner Python. Let me just write a small Python script instead.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"..."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_lpcwpddkxyAEmZyjqbeM8807","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && python -c \"import urllib.request; req=urllib.request.Request('http://127.0.0.1:10280/'); resp=urllib.request.urlopen(req,timeout=10); html=resp.read().decode('utf-8',errors='replace'); tags = [l for l in html.splitlines() if 'ASTROHUB:' in l or 'advanced' in l.lower() or 'renderAdvResult' in l]; print('\\n'.join(tags[:20]))\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":53414,"output":194,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53608,"cost":{"input":0.053413999999999996,"output":0.0006208,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.054034799999999994}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782675406970,"responseId":"cht000d2a8a@dx19f0fbc0149b894652"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f85efac2","parentId":"b6e77ed0","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:36:51.166Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_lpcwpddkxyAEmZyjqbeM8807","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/* --- Advanced Page: Left Sidebar Layout --- */\r\n        .advanced-layout { display:flex; gap:0; min-height:600px; }\r\n        .advanced-sidebar { width:200px; background:#161b22; border-right:1px solid #21262d; padding:8px 0; flex-shrink:0; }\r\n        .advanced-sidebar .sidebar-item { background:none; border:none; color:#8b949e; padding:10px 16px; cursor:pointer; font-size:13px; transition:all 0.2s; width:100%; text-align:left; display:block; }\r\n        .advanced-sidebar .sidebar-item:hover { background:#21262d; color:#e0e6f0; }\r\n        .advanced-sidebar .sidebar-item.active { background:#238636; color:#fff; border-left:3px solid #3fb950; }\r\n        .advanced-content { flex:1; min-width:0; padding:20px; }\r\n        .advanced-content .page { display:none; }\r\n        .advanced-content .page.active { display:block; }\r\n        /* Advanced page status panel */\r\n        .advanced-status-panel { background:#0d1117; border:1px solid #21262d; border-radius:10px; padding:16px; margin:16px 0; }\r\n        .advanced-status-panel h4 { font-size:15px; color:#e0e6f0; margin-bottom:12px; border-bottom:1px solid #21262d; padding-bottom:8px; }\r\n        <!-- Advanced Features: У׼ ���ܲ��� ��λ���� �ٶȲ��� ����/�洢 -->\r\n        <button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"advanced\">�߼�����</button>\r\n    document.querySelector('[data-page=\"advanced\"]').click();\r\n<div class=\"page\" id=\"page-advanced\">\r\n        'function': '/api/v1/advanced/function/run',\r\n        'limit': '/api/v1/advanced/limit/run',\r\n        'speed': '/api/v1/advanced/speed/run',\r\n    var detectApiUrl = '/api/v1/advanced/detect/start';"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":587,"aggregated":"/* --- Advanced Page: Left Sidebar Layout --- */\r\n        .advanced-layout { display:flex; gap:0; min-height:600px; }\r\n        .advanced-sidebar { width:200px; background:#161b22; border-right:1px solid #21262d; padding:8px 0; flex-shrink:0; }\r\n        .advanced-sidebar .sidebar-item { background:none; border:none; color:#8b949e; padding:10px 16px; cursor:pointer; font-size:13px; transition:all 0.2s; width:100%; text-align:left; display:block; }\r\n        .advanced-sidebar .sidebar-item:hover { background:#21262d; color:#e0e6f0; }\r\n        .advanced-sidebar .sidebar-item.active { background:#238636; color:#fff; border-left:3px solid #3fb950; }\r\n        .advanced-content { flex:1; min-width:0; padding:20px; }\r\n        .advanced-content .page { display:none; }\r\n        .advanced-content .page.active { display:block; }\r\n        /* Advanced page status panel */\r\n        .advanced-status-panel { background:#0d1117; border:1px solid #21262d; border-radius:10px; padding:16px; margin:16px 0; }\r\n        .advanced-status-panel h4 { font-size:15px; color:#e0e6f0; margin-bottom:12px; border-bottom:1px solid #21262d; padding-bottom:8px; }\r\n        <!-- Advanced Features: У׼ ���ܲ��� ��λ���� �ٶȲ��� ����/�洢 -->\r\n        <button class=\"nav-btn\" data-page=\"advanced\">�߼�����</button>\r\n    document.querySelector('[data-page=\"advanced\"]').click();\r\n<div class=\"page\" id=\"page-advanced\">\r\n        'function': '/api/v1/advanced/function/run',\r\n        'limit': '/api/v1/advanced/limit/run',\r\n        'speed': '/api/v1/advanced/speed/run',\r\n    var detectApiUrl = '/api/v1/advanced/detect/start';","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782675411166}}
{"type":"message","id":"f03dfb95","parentId":"f85efac2","timestamp":"2026-06-28T19:37:03.176Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" 响应Good, the advanced.html content is being served as part of the main index.html page (via template inclusion). The `renderAdvResult` function is there. Now let me check if `advanced.html` renders as the template—it seems `<div class=\"page\" id=\"page-advanced\">` is present. Let me check how the HTML template includes this.\n\nThe key question is: does the backend's `advanced.html` template include match what we see in the page? Let me check the template mechanism.\n\nLooking at the search results, I can see the page contains:\n- `renderAdvResult` - this is the function in `advanced.html` ✅\n- CSS for `advanced-layout`, `advanced-sidebar`, etc. ✅\n- `data-page=\"advanced\"` page ✅\n- `speed: '/api/v1/advanced/speed/run'` - the API map ✅\n- `var detectApiUrl = '/api/v1/advanced/detect/start'` ✅\n\nBut I need to verify: is the page serving advanced.html as embedded in index.html, or does it serve it separately? Let me check how the main.py serves this page.\n\nActually, looking at the output - all the advanced.html content is in the page. The `advanced.html` is included as a template. The `renderAdvResult` function in it already handles the speed case at line 408: `else if (results.speed_map !== undefined || results.pan_speed !== undefined)`.\n\nWith our fix in `router.py` the `detect/start` returns `results[\"speed\"] = _format_speed_results(speed_result)` which contains `speed_map` and `pan_speed`. So `renderAdvResult` in `advanced.html` will match the `else if` condition and render the speed table.\n\nThe fix looks complete. Let me verify the complete data flow:\n\n1. User clicks \"开始测试\" on Advanced page → `runAdvTest()` → POST `/advanced/detect/start`\n2. Backend `advanced_detect_start` runs `SpeedTester.run_all_tests()` → returns `list[dict]` \n3. **FIX**: `_format_speed_results(speed_result)` converts list → `{speed_map, pan_speed, tilt_speed, by_zoom, total_tests}`\n4. Stored as `results[\"speed\"] = speed_formatted`\n5. Poll `fetchResult(taskId)` → GET `/advanced/detect/result/{task_id}` → `data.results.speed` = formatted dict\n6. `renderAdvResult(testResult)` → matches `results.speed_map !== undefined` → renders speed table ✅\n\nThis should fix the \"项目 支持 范围\" display issue. Let me summarize the report for the boss.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 报告 v7.119\n\n### 问题根因\n\n**高级测试页面走的是不同 API 路径**，返回格式不同：\n\n```\n主控台: POST /advanced/speed/run  → _format_speed_results() → {speed_map, pan_speed, ...} ✅\n高级测试: POST /advanced/detect/start → run_all_tests() → list[{axis, speed_level, ...}] ❌ 未分组\n                                                              ↓\n                                           renderAdvResult 拿不到 speed_map → 掉进 else\n                                                              ↓\n                                           当功能测试渲染 → \"项目 支持 范围 0 N -~- ...\"\n```\n\n### 修复\n\n| 文件 | 改动 |\n|------|------|\n| `router.py:2739` | 新增 `_format_speed_results()` 公共函数 |\n| `router.py:2666` | `/advanced/speed/run` 复用公共函数（替换内联38行） |\n| `router.py:2860` | `/advanced/detect/start` 速度分支调用 `_format_speed_results()` |\n| `advanced.html:842` | `fetchResult` 进度计数改用 `total_tests`（修复速度时 `Object.keys().length` = 6 而非真实测试数） |\n\n### 数据流（修复后）\n\n```\nPOST /advanced/detect/start\n  └→ SpeedTester.run_all_tests() → list[{axis, speed_level, zoom, speed_val, ...}]\n      └→ _format_speed_results(list) → {speed_map, pan_speed, tilt_speed, by_zoom, total_tests}\n          └→ results[\"speed\"] = formatted\n              └→ fetchResult → renderAdvResult({speed_map, pan_speed, ...})\n                  └→ 匹配 speed 分支 → 渲染速度表 ✅\n```\n\n### 验证\n\n```\nrouter.py 语法 ✅\n_advanced/detect/start 速度分组 ✅\nadvanced.html fetchResult 计数修复 ✅\n备份 → backup_20260629_speed_fix/ ✅\n```\n\n需要启动测试验证高级测试页面的速度显示吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":54107,"output":1043,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55150,"cost":{"input":0.054106999999999995,"output":0.0033376000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0574446}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782675411168,"responseId":"cht000d56fc@dx19f0fbc11c9ba5e452"}}
