{"type":"message","id":"07617a7c","parentId":"8858dcbb","timestamp":"2026-06-28T20:18:48.846Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good - after cleanup, the only remaining endpoints related to speed/limit/function/detect are:\n\n1. `/advanced/detect/start` - the unified detection API\n2. `/advanced/detect/status/{task_id}` - polling\n3. `/advanced/detect/result/{task_id}` - get results\n4. `/advanced/detect/cancel/{task_id}` - cancel\n5. `/ptz/{device_id}/function` - device function detection (different, image-related)\n\nAnd the frontend has:\n- `renderAdvResult()` - 1 function\n- `runAdvTest()` - 1 function\n- `/advanced/detect` - 4 refs (start, status, result, cancel)\n\nSo after cleanup, there's exactly ONE branch for speed/limit/function testing: `advanced.html → /advanced/detect/start → renderAdvResult()`.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"清理后：\n\n## 当前分支：1条\n\n```\nadvanced.html → /advanced/detect/start → _format_speed_results() → renderAdvResult()\n```\n\n### 后端端点（4个，同一套）\n\n| 端点 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| `/advanced/detect/start` | 启动检测 |\n| `/advanced/detect/status/{task_id}` | 轮询进度 |\n| `/advanced/detect/result/{task_id}` | 获取结果 |\n| `/advanced/detect/cancel/{task_id}` | 取消 |\n\n### 前端函数（2个）\n\n| 函数 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| `runAdvTest()` | 发起检测 |\n| `renderAdvResult()` | 渲染结果（speed/limit/function 共用） |\n\n无分支，无重复。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":108139,"output":359,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108498,"cost":{"input":0.108139,"output":0.0011488000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1092878}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782677917985,"responseId":"cht000d9746@dx19f0fe2517cb8ab162"}}
