{"type":"message","id":"54fe48f0","parentId":"bee9b893","timestamp":"2026-06-28T20:31:48.392Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" 响应`advConnectDevice` 是动态创建的 `<select>`，`onConnectDeviceChange` 函数没有被 `onchange` 绑定引用。让我进一步确认...\n\n```python\n# Check if advConnectDevice select exists in HTML or is dynamically created\n# Already found: it's dynamically built in populateDeviceSelects()\n\n# Check if any onchange handler refers to onConnectDeviceChange\n```\n\nLet me check the full HTML page and see what onchange handler is on advConnectDevice. Also need to check if `onConnectDeviceChange` is truly dead - is it referenced from any onclick/onchange attribute or addEventListener?","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"`onConnectDeviceChange` 没有被任何 `onchange` 绑定。确认是否死函数："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_tkqk2EctzYA6odvKCIwb3061","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && python -c \"\nhtml=open('src/web/index.html',encoding='utf-8').read()\n# Find ALL references to onConnectDeviceChange\nc=html.count('onConnectDeviceChange')\nprint(f'Total refs: {c}')\n# Check if it's called via any event handler pattern\nimport re\nfor m in re.finditer(r'(?:onchange|onclick|addEventListener)[^>]*onConnect', html):\n    print(f'Event binding: {m.group()[:100]}')\n# Check if populateDeviceSelects sets onchange\nidx=html.find('function populateDeviceSelects')\npop_chunk=html[idx:idx+1000]\nfor m in re.finditer(r'onchange|onConnect|advConnectDevice', pop_chunk):\n    ctx=pop_chunk[max(0,m.start()-20):m.end()+50]\n    print(f'populateDeviceSelects: {repr(ctx[:120])}')\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":113689,"output":412,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114101,"cost":{"input":0.113689,"output":0.0013184000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1150074}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782678702090