{"type":"message","id":"3fbc636a","parentId":"cfcea562","timestamp":"2026-06-28T21:10:38.777Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" 响应Now I see the problem. The `replay.html` file defines its own `closeModal` function which conflicts with the `showModal` component's `closeModal` function defined in `index.html`. When replay's `closeModal` gets overwritten by `index.html`'s `closeModal` (which only handles `#astroModal`), the replay close button stops working.\n\nLet me check the `showModal` component's `closeModal` to understand the conflict:","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"问题找到了。`replay.html` 定义了自己的 `window.closeModal = function()` 处理回放大图关闭，但 `index.html` 的 `showModal` 组件也定义了 `window.closeModal`，后者覆盖了前者——导致回放大图 × 按钮调用的是弹窗组件的 `closeModal`，找不到 `#replay-modal`。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_fkgDEeTKcNjjjw27ssKq2291","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"offset":447,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":143257,"output":276,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":143533,"cost":{"input":0.143257,"output":0.0008832000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1441402}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782681033261,"responseId":"cht000f21d3@dx19f1011dbf9ba5d452"}}
