{"type":"message","id":"37001e13","parentId":"9b38f06f","timestamp":"2026-06-28T21:40:31.291Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_ChRm65T3NcOPtlAyTzH43498","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[32;1mLineNumber[0m[32;1m Line[0m\r\n[32;1m----------[0m [32;1m----[0m\r\n       828         function presetGoto() {\r\n       844         function presetSet() {\r\n       953         function ptzGotoSelectedPreset() {\r\n       972         function ptzSetSelectedPreset() {\r\n       993         function ptzWritePreset() {\r\n      1624         function ptzHome() {"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":399,"aggregated":"[32;1mLineNumber[0m[32;1m Line[0m\r\n[32;1m----------[0m [32;1m----[0m\r\n       828         function presetGoto() {\r\n       844         function presetSet() {\r\n       953         function ptzGotoSelectedPreset() {\r\n       972         function ptzSetSelectedPreset() {\r\n       993         function ptzWritePreset() {\r\n      1624         function ptzHome() {","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782682831291}}
{"type":"message","id":"4cf431c0","parentId":"37001e13","timestamp":"2026-06-28T21:40:41.152Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the issues:\n\n1. **Preset buttons**: \"保存\" (ptzSetSelectedPreset) and \"写入\" (ptzWritePreset) are both doing similar things - saving a preset. \"保存\" uses the dropdown value, \"写入\" uses a modal. Need to keep \"写入\" and remove \"保存\". Also need to merge 归位/保存/前往/下拉 into one row.\n\n2. **Status messages**: \"已归位\" \"已前往预置点10\" etc. are shown in `ptzPresetResult` div - should go to operation log (addLog) instead.\n\n3. **Scrollbars**: Need hidden scrollbars on console dropdown, operation log, media info, and advanced test info panels.\n\nLet me read the relevant JS functions first.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"...\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_lpc2ylah591jodf4j20nmtzi","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":828,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":147031,"output":266,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":147297,"cost":{"input":0.147031,"output":0.0008512000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1478822}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782682831299,"responseId":"cht000d8f93@dx19f102d4a68b8ab162"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2bef85eb","parentId":"4cf431c0","timestamp":"2026-06-28T21:40:41.202Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_lpc2ylah591jodf4j20nmtzi","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        function presetGoto() {\r\n            var deviceIp = document.getElementById('advConnectDevice').value;\r\n            var presetId = parseInt(document.getElementById('presetIdInput').value) || 10;\r\n            if (!deviceIp) { showToast('warning', '请先选择设备'); return; }\r\n            var resultDiv = document.getElementById('presetResult');\r\n            resultDiv.textContent = '调用预置点 ' + presetId + '...';\r\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/preset/' + presetId, null).then(function(resp) {\r\n                if (resp && resp.success !== false) {\r\n                    resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#3fb950\">✅ 已调用预置点 ' + presetId + '</span>';\r\n                } else {\r\n                    resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#f85149\">❌ 调用失败: ' + (resp ? resp.message : '未知') + '</span>';\r\n                }\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#f85149\">❌ 异常: ' + e.message + '</span>';\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n        function presetSet() {\r\n            var deviceIp = document.getElementById('advConnectDevice').value;\r\n            var presetId = parseInt(document.getElementById('presetIdInput').value) || 10;\r\n            if (!deviceIp) { showToast('warning', '请先选择设备'); return; }\r\n            var resultDiv = document.getElementById('presetResult');\r\n            resultDiv.textContent = '设置预置点 ' + presetId + '...';\r\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/preset/' + presetId + '/set', null).then(function(resp) {\r\n                if (resp && resp.success) {\r\n                    resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#3fb950\">✅ 已设置预置点 ' + presetId + '</span>';\r\n                } else {\r\n                    resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#f85149\">❌ 设置失败: ' + (resp ? resp.message : '未知') + '</span>';\r\n                }\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#f85149\">❌ 异常: ' + e.message + '</span>';\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n        // 渲染完整检测结果到连接设备页面\r\n        function renderConnectFullResults(results, type) {\r\n            var area = document.getElementById('connectFullResultArea');\r\n            var noResult = document.getElementById('connectNoResult');\r\n            if (!area) return;\r\n            area.style.display = 'block';\r\n            noResult.style.display = 'none';\r\n            var html = '<div style=\"margin-top:16px\">';\r\n            html += '<h4 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#e0e6f0;margin-bottom:12px;padding-bottom:8px;border-bottom:1px solid #21262d\">';\r\n            if (type === 'function') html += '🔍 功能检测完整结果';\r\n            else if (type === 'limit') html += '📐 限位检测完整结果';\r\n            else if (type === 'speed') html += '⚡ 速度检测完整结果';\r\n            else html += '检测结果';\r\n            html += '</h4>';\r\n            if (type === 'function') {\r\n                var funcData = results.functions || results;\r\n                html += '<table class=\"result-table\"><thead><tr><th>功能</th><th>支持</th><th>最小值</th><th>最大值</th><th>当前值</th><th>状态</th></tr></thead><tbody>';\r\n                var keys = Object.keys(funcData);\r\n                if (keys.length === 0) {\r\n                    html += '<tr><td colspan=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;color:#6e7681\">暂无结果</td></tr>';\r\n                } else {\r\n                    keys.forEach(function(key) {\r\n                        var item = funcData[key];\r\n                        if (!item || typeof item !== 'object' || !item.hasOwnProperty('supported')) return;\r\n                        var supported = item.supported ? '<span class=\"badge yes\">✅</span>' : '<span class=\"badge no\">❌</span>';\r\n                        var status = item.status || '完成';\r\n                        html += '<tr>';\r\n                        html += '<td>' + key + '</td>';\r\n                        html += '<td>' + supported + '</td>';\r\n                        html += '<td>' + (item.min_value != null ? item.min_value : '--') + '</td>';\r\n                        html += '<td>' + (item.max_value != null ? item.max_value : '--') + '</td>';\r\n                        html += '<td>' + (item.current_value != null ? item.current_value : '--') + '</td>';\r\n                        html += '<td><span class=\"badge yes\">' + status + '</span></td>';\r\n                        html += '</tr>';\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n                html += '</tbody></table>';\r\n            } else if (type === 'limit') {\r\n                html += '<div class=\"advanced-status-panel\">';\r\n                html += '<div class=\"status-row\"><span class=\"status-label\">P轴限位</span><span class=\"status-value\">' + results.pan_min + ' ~ ' + results.pan_max + '</span></div>';\r\n                html += '<div class=\"status-row\"><span class=\"status-label\">T轴限位</span><span class=\"status-value\">' + results.tilt_min + ' ~ ' + results.tilt_max + '</span></div>';\r\n                html += '<div class=\"status-row\"><span class=\"status-label\">Z轴限位</span><span class=\"status-value\">' + results.zoom_min + ' ~ ' + results.zoom_max + '</span></div>';\r\n                html += '<div class=\"status-row\"><span class=\"status-label\">翻转</span><span class=\"status-value\">' + (results.has_flip ? '有' : '无') + '</span></div>';\r\n                html += '<div class=\"status-row\"><span class=\"status-label\">稳定性</span><span class=\"status-value\">' + (results.stability_check ? '<span class=\"badge yes\">✅ 稳定</span>' : '<span class=\"badge no\">❌ 不稳定</span>') + '</span></div>';\r\n                if (results.csv_path) html += '<div class=\"status-row\"><span class=\"status-label\">CSV 路径</span><span class=\"status-value\">' + results.csv_path + '</span></div>';\r\n                html += '</div>';\r\n            } else if (type === 'speed') {\r\n                var byZoom = results.by_zoom || {};\r\n\n[1946 more lines in file. Use offset=908 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782682841202}}
{"type":"message","id":"cf527768","parentId":"2bef85eb","timestamp":"2026-06-28T21:40:48.738Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me check the ptzGotoSelectedPreset, ptzSetSelectedPreset, ptzWritePreset, and ptzHome functions:","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"...\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_868puv71pxo5f0hifiyo5y2i","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":950,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"sf","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":148770,"output":131,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":148901,"cost":{"input":0.14876999999999999,"output":0.00041920000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1491892}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782682841207,"responseId":"cht000d531e@dx19f102d713ab958312"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b37e4fa1","parentId":"cf527768","timestamp":"2026-06-28T21:40:48.784Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_868puv71pxo5f0hifiyo5y2i","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                if (resultDiv) resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#f85149\">获取失败: ' + e.message + '</span>';\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n        function ptzGotoSelectedPreset() {\r\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice.ip;\r\n            var sel = document.getElementById('ptzPresetSelect');\r\n            var presetId = parseInt(sel.value);\r\n            if (!dev) { showToast('warning', '请先选择设备'); return; }\r\n            if (!presetId) { showToast('warning', '请先选择预置点'); return; }\r\n            var resultDiv = document.getElementById('ptzPresetResult');\r\n            resultDiv.textContent = '跳转到预置点 ' + presetId + '...';\r\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/preset/' + presetId, null).then(function(resp) {\r\n                if (resp && resp.success !== false) {\r\n                    resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#3fb950\">✅ 已前往预置点 ' + presetId + '</span>';\r\n                    if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('预置点: 前往 #' + presetId, 'success');\r\n                } else {\r\n                    resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#f85149\">❌ 跳转失败: ' + (resp ? resp.message : '未知') + '</span>';\r\n                }\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#f85149\">❌ 异常: ' + e.message + '</span>';\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n        function ptzSetSelectedPreset() {\r\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice.ip;\r\n            var sel = document.getElementById('ptzPresetSelect');\r\n            var presetId = parseInt(sel.value);\r\n            if (!dev) { showToast('warning', '请先选择设备'); return; }\r\n            if (!presetId) { showToast('warning', '请先选择预置点编号'); return; }\r\n            var resultDiv = document.getElementById('ptzPresetResult');\r\n            resultDiv.textContent = '保存当前位置为预置点 ' + presetId + '...';\r\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/preset/' + presetId + '/set', null).then(function(resp) {\r\n                if (resp && resp.success) {\r\n                    resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#3fb950\">✅ 已保存预置点 ' + presetId + '</span>';\r\n                    if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('预置点: 保存 #' + presetId, 'success');\r\n                    loadPresetList(); // refresh\r\n                } else {\r\n                    resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#f85149\">❌ 保存失败: ' + (resp ? resp.message : '未知') + '</span>';\r\n                }\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#f85149\">❌ 异常: ' + e.message + '</span>';\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n        // v7.117: 写入预置点 — 弹窗输入编号+名称\r\n        function ptzWritePreset() {\r\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n            if (!dev) { showToast('warning', '请先连接设备'); return; }\r\n            showModal({\r\n                type: 'form',\r\n                title: '写入预置点',\r\n                fields: [\r\n                    { id:'presetId', label:'预置点编号', value:'', placeholder:'1-300', required:true },\r\n                    { id:'presetName', label:'名称', value:'', placeholder:'选填' }\r\n                ],\r\n                onConfirm: function(data) {\r\n                    var presetId = parseInt(data.presetId);\r\n                    var presetName = (data.presetName || '').trim();\r\n                    if (!presetId || presetId < 1 || presetId > 300) {\r\n                        showToast('error', '预置点编号需在 1-300 之间');\r\n                        return;\r\n                    }\r\n                    var resultDiv = document.getElementById('ptzPresetResult');\r\n                    if (resultDiv) resultDiv.textContent = '写入预置点 ' + presetId + '...';\r\n                    var url = '/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/preset/' + presetId + '/set';\r\n                    if (presetName) url += '?name=' + encodeURIComponent(presetName);\r\n                    apiPost(url, null).then(function(resp) {\r\n                        if (resp && resp.success) {\r\n                            if (resultDiv) resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#3fb950\">✅ 已写入预置点 ' + presetId + (presetName ? ' (' + presetName + ')' : '') + '</span>';\r\n                            if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('预置点: 写入 #' + presetId + (presetName ? ' ' + presetName : ''), 'success');\r\n                            loadPresetList();\r\n                        } else {\r\n                            if (resultDiv) resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#f85149\">❌ 写入失败: ' + (resp ? resp.message : '未知') + '</span>';\r\n                        }\r\n                    }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                        if (resultDiv) resultDiv.innerHTML = '<span style=\"color:#f85149\">❌ 异常: ' + e.message + '</span>';\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n        function findMacByIP(ip) {\r\n            var dev = allDevices.find(function(d) { return d.ip === ip; });\r\n\n[1824 more lines in file. Use offset=1030 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782682848784}}
