{"type":"compaction","id":"5cfad71d","parentId":"6d72af8c","timestamp":"2026-06-28T21:45:43.341Z","summary":"## Goal\n修复 AstroHub 速度测试结果在高级测试页面显示错误（显示\"项目 支持 范围\"表格而非速度数据），审计并清理死代码和硬编码敏感信息。\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- 老板要求最小改动，不要无谓分支\n- 需要完整审计报告后评审再执行\n- 备份在 `backup_20260629_speed_fix/`\n- 只删不改，禁止引入新功能\n- 禁止打补丁，必须精确删除\n- 备份后清理，迭代版本号\n- 需要设计全量测试脚本验证所有功能正常\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] v7.118 修复：`router.py` 中 `/advanced/speed/run` 将 list 分组为 `{speed_map, pan_speed, tilt_speed, by_zoom}`；`index.html` 失败时显示错误\n- [x] v7.119 修复：`advanced.html` 的 `renderAdvResult` 添加 Zoom 交叉表渲染；`renderConnectFullResults` speed 分支同步更新\n- [x] 发现根因：`advanced.html` → `/advanced/detect/start` 直接存 `run_all_tests()` 原始 list，未做 `_format_speed_results()` 分组\n- [x] 提取 `_format_speed_results()` 公共函数，两条路径复用\n- [x] `advanced.html` 中 `fetchResult` 进度计数改用 `total_tests`\n- [x] 第一轮审计 `_audit.py` 运行完成（但 body 检查太宽泛，JS 函数体也被匹配）\n- [x] 第二轮精确审计 `_audit2.py`：排除 `<script>` 块，仅检查 HTML `id=` 属性\n- [x] 第三轮审计 `_audit3.py`：检查 Jinja2 includes 和页面加载机制\n- [x] 审计完成：确认 13 个死 JS 函数\n- [x] 确认 3 个死 Python 端点（/advanced/function/run, /advanced/limit/run, /advanced/speed/run + cancel/status）\n- [x] 确认 3 个死 Pydantic 模型\n- [x] 确认 advanced.html 中 apiMap 为死代码\n- [x] 备份到 backup_20260629_clean/\n- [x] router.py 死端点 + 死模型已删除\n- [x] advanced.html apiMap 已删除\n- [x] index.html 精确删除：从 `// Function Detection (P4.1-P4.21)` 到 `// 一键检测` 前（L742-L1145），删除 23681 chars\n- [x] 活函数验证通过：startDetection, runDetectionStep, finishDetection, addDetectionLog, presetGoto, presetSet, renderConnectFullResults, loadPresetList 等全部保留\n- [x] index.html `_expose` 数组已清理：删除 funcDetectRun, funcDetectRestore, limitTestRun, speedTestRun, connectFuncDetectRun, connectSpeedTestRun 六个死引用\n- [x] router.py 语法验证通过 (ast.parse OK)\n- [x] AstroHub 已重启（headless 模式），127.0.0.1:10280 返回 200\n- [x] 全量活函数验证通过：所有 35 个活函数在 index.html 中均存在\n- [x] 死代码扫描完成：14 个死函数引用已确认全部清除\n- [x] 页面切换逻辑验证通过：navbarSwitch, showPage, \n\n[Compaction summary truncated to fit budget]\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Goal\nThe user wants to write and run a comprehensive E2E test script for AstroHub that tests browser interactions including tab switching, PTZ controls, WASM stream playback, device connect/disconnect, SADP device discovery, advanced test (detect/start/stop), replay page, and settings configuration. The script must include reasonable timeout settings to avoid SIGKILL interruptions.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Must use reasonable timeout settings to prevent SIGKILL\n- Test against running AstroHub instance at `http://127.0.0.1:10280`\n- Test script should be in `C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub`\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Verified one device available at `192.168.5.72` (4k 32X DC) via API call to `/api/v1/devices`\n- [x] Confirmed Playwright is available in the Python environment\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Writing the comprehensive E2E test script\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Use Playwright for browser automation**: The initial non-browser approach via API calls was insufficient; Playwright was confirmed available and chosen for simulating actual browser interactions\n- **First API syntax error fixed**: Initial Python one-liner had escaped-quote SyntaxError; corrected to single-line format for device discovery check\n- **Test scope**: Covers navigation, PTZ (move/home/stop), WASM streams, device management, SADP discovery, advanced test flow, replay, and settings\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Write the comprehensive Playwright-based E2E test script\n2. Include timeout configurations (e.g., `browser_context.set_default_timeout()`, page-level timeouts)\n3. Run the test script and verify results\n4. Ensure all test cases pass or report failures clearly\n\n## Critical Context\n- AstroHub running on `http://127.0.0.1:10280`\n- Device IP: `192.168.5.72`, name: `4k 32X DC`\n- API devices endpoint: `GET http://127.0.0.1:10280/api/v1/devices`\n- Working directory: `C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\de